 e. Come as you are\, dress how you feel\, and bring your boldest ideas\,\,
  you never know who you'll be working with next. Let's make this a summer 
 to remember.\n\nFashion Forward is a NYC-based community connecting fashio
 n founders\, designers\, photographers\, stylists\, and creative leaders t
 hrough curated experiences that favor depth\, quality\, and real connectio
 n over crowded rooms.\n\nBy RSVP’ing\, you agree to receive occasional m
