SUMMARY:"DEAR DESIGNER\," by Otherkind: THE PRELUDE
LOCATION:Brooklyn\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n"Dear Designer\," will be a pop-up installation
  in NYC where we are exhibiting love letters to design from designers arou
 nd the world. \n\nAhead of our main event happening in late July (TBA)\, w
 e are hosting THE PRELUDE  — an intimate letter-writing event to offer a
  space for reflection and mingling among designers. Letters and messages h
 andwritten at this event will have the opportunity to be featured in the i
 nstallation. \n\nJoin us for a cozy session to slow down and reflect about
  our creative practices. Light bites and drinks will be provided alongside
  paper/supplies for writing\, but feel free to bring your own. \n\nLocatio
 n is in Williamsburg at a studio space near Bushwick Inlet Park. Spots lim
 ited. \n\nAGENDA\n6:30pm - Doors Open\n7:00pm - Intros & Writing\n8:30pm -
  Wrap up & Close\n\nCalendar: Otherkind\n\nHosts: kelly :)\, Otherkind\n\n
 Event page: https://luma.com/2br0m0fc
