SUMMARY:AI Builders Night New York
LOCATION:LOFT39\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin us in New York at Loft 39 for an evening d
 edicated to the builders behind modern AI. From real-world use cases to th
 e infrastructure powering large-scale systems\, AI Night brings together e
 ngineers\, data practitioners\, and founders shaping how AI is built and d
 eployed today. Brought to you by ClickHouse and Docker!\n\nCurrent Agenda:
 \n\n5:00 PM: Arrivals\, Check-In and Networking\n\n5:50 PM: Welcome and In
 troductions + Food and Drink\n\n5:55 - 6:20PM: Thomas Holvoet Co-Founder &
  CTO @ Converge\n\n6:20 - 6:45 PM: Mike Toscano\, Engineering Manager @ P
 aylocity\n\n6:45 - 7:10 PM:\n\n7:30 - 8:30 PM: Q&A\, Networking\n\n8:30 PM
 : Meetup Concludes\n\nCalendar: ClickHouse Events\n\nHosts: Zoe Steinkamp\
 n\nVenue: LOFT39\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/clickh-lz8k
URL:https://luma.com/clickh-lz8k
