SUMMARY:MáLà Project x Odd One In Present: The Spiciest Supper Club
LOCATION:MáLà Project Midtown East\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nReady to ditch the swipe life and spark real co
 nnections over dry pot?\n\nMáLà Project × Odd One In present The Spicie
 st Supper Club. Love at First Spice for 32 of New York's hottest singles. 
 Rotate through four hand-matched rounds—each course unleashing a daring 
 spicy-challenge and cheeky prompts straight from Odd One In’s cult-favor
 ite cards. Feast on MáLà Project's crafted 4-course menu\, dodge small t
 alk with surprise twists at every bite\, and let unhinged fun spark real c
 onnections. Bring your appetite for flavor and flirts—this is dinner wit
 h a little spice.\n\nPlease note: This event is non-refundable.\n\n[Please
  show some love! Remember to tip staff\, tip your bartender.]\n\nIf you ha
 ve any food allergies\, kindly include them in the notes at checkout. Sinc
 e this event features multiple rotating courses\, clear communication is i
 mportant to ensure your safety.\n\nIf you have any questions\, don’t hes
 itate to call us at (212) 602-1005 or email [party@malaproject.com].\n\nPr
 ice includes ticket\, tax\, and service fee.\n\nCalendar: MáLà Project\n
 \nHosts: Julie Zhu\, leilei\, Gloria Liu\n\nVenue: MáLà Project Midtown 
 East\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/1yinpuet
URL:https://luma.com/1yinpuet
