SUMMARY:Cake Decorating Workshop 🍰
LOCATION:519 Broome St 2nd floor\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nAt Maayan’s Patisserie\, cake decorating beco
 mes a celebratory\, design-led hospitality experience set within an intima
 te\, candlelit\, vintage European dinner-party atmosphere in the heart of 
 SoHo\, New York.\n\nAs part of the experience\, each guest receives:\n\nA 
 glass of wine 🥂\n\nThree (3) vanilla cake layers 🍰\n\nVanilla frosti
 ng 🍨\n\nDecorative fruits 🍇\n\nA piping practice sheet 📜\n\nCake-
 building & decorating supplies 🥄\n\nThis experience is completely begin
 ner-friendly! You’ll learn everything you need to know from scratch (the
  filling\, coating\, and vintage piping techniques).\n\n*Perfectionists 
 — please come with compassion. Your first time frosting may feel funky a
 nd imperfect\, and that’s part of the magic. You’re here to try someth
 ing new and have a beautiful time ✨\n\nYou’ll build and decorate your 
 own individual cake\, then pack it up to enjoy later at home with your lov
 ed ones! Cakes are not eaten during the event\, and no outside food or bev
 erages are allowed.\n\nCan’t wait to host you\,\n\nMaayan’s Team 💖\
 n\n@maayanspatisserie by @maayanadin\n\nCancellation Policy\n\nTickets for
  this event are non-refundable and non-exchangeable. Please double-check y
 our calendar before purchasing. If you can no longer attend\, you’re wel
 come to transfer your ticket to someone else.\n\nAccessibility\n\nAs we ar
 e located in an old building\, there is no elevator\, and stairs lead to t
 he experience. If you have any physical accessibility needs\, we would lov
 e to welcome you at our ADA-compliant experience\, Maayan’s Pottery.\n\n
 Photography Disclaimer\n\nWhile we strive to keep photography and videogra
 phy to a minimum\, all guests consent to being photographed and filmed. Th
 ese materials may be used for marketing and promotional purposes at the di
 scretion of Maayan Adin.\n\nFor questions\, email contact@maayanadin.com\n
 \nCalendar: Maayan's Hospitality Group\n\nHosts: Maayan's Hospitality Grou
 p\n\nVenue: 519 Broome St 2nd floor\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/7724o3
 g7
URL:https://luma.com/7724o3g7
