SUMMARY:DOTC Desi Island Singles Night: NYC
LOCATION:New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nY'all have been asking and we're delivering.\n\
 nWe've got the whole space to ourselves at one of NYC's newest spots and w
 e're doing what we do best\, bringing South Asian singles together for a n
 ight that actually makes sense. (Do you know how hard it is to lock down a
  venue in this city?)\n\nThis is the low-key\, low-stress way to meet othe
 r South Asian singles who actually get it. No matchmaking. No speed dating
 .\n\nNo host. No forced mixers. No awkward icebreakers.\n\nJust a room ful
 l of people who are looking for the same thing... meet someone in NYC who 
 is South Asian\, cool\, and like-minded.\n\nOh\, and your ticket comes wit
 h a Chaat Dog. Yes\, really.\n\nThere's a DJ. There are available drinks. 
 And there are people who showed up on purpose.\n\nCome with your friends. 
 Come solo. Either way\, everyone's starting from the same place.\n\nSpace 
 is limited. This is DOTC ticketed only\, which means everyone here knows e
 xactly what they signed up for.\n\nSee you July 10th\, NYC. 9 PM - 1 AM.\n
 \n----\n\nDose of Travel Club is your favorite South Asian travel and soci
 al club where we curate experiences\, events\, and find you your people. D
 OTC app coming soon ♡ Our upcoming trips are to Barbados\, Pakistan\, Pe
 ru\, Kenya\, Japan\, Bali & more!\n\nNo refunds. If you can't make it\, pl
 ease update your RSVP so we can manage the room and make sure it's the bes
 t experience for everyone. Thank you ♡ By attending\, you acknowledge ph
 otos/videos may be taken for promotional purposes\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\
 nHosts: Dose Of Travel Club\, Anushka Verma\n\nEvent page: https://luma.co
 m/uac59ygi
URL:https://luma.com/uac59ygi
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
