SUMMARY:Ren Faire Inspired Artist Market - "Analog Renaissance" by Offline 
 Recess
LOCATION:Sweet Fire Cafe & Studio\, Kings County\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nYou are cordially invited to our 📚Analog Ren
 aissance📚 artist market\, workshop\, and sticker swap event!\n\nJoin us
  for a TWO DAY event celebrating the revival of analog practices\, all thi
 ngs handmade\, communal\, and most importantly - offline! We will have 20+
  vendors\, stickers\, prints\, jewelry\, zines\, accessories\, stationery\
 , a raffle to raise fund for future events\, a costume connection activity
  with prizes\, a stamp rally with prizes\, and our beloved sticker swap.\n
 \nFree entry\, no ticket needed—just RSVP so we know how many people to 
 expect!\n\n⏰ When: July 11th & 12th\, 12-6pm\n\n📍 Where: 338 Broadway
 \, Brooklyn NY\n\n🎊 What: Artist Market\, Workshops\, Sticker Swap! Com
 e dressed up in your best ren faire attire to possibly collect a prize and
  connect with others :)\n\n❣️ Important: KN95 (or better) respirator m
 asks are required to attend the event! We will have cute and colorful mask
 s provided at the entrance\, as well as a designated area by the entrance 
 to briefly snack (away from the vendor area) if needed. If we are able to 
 secure purifiers provided by A.I.R. NYC\, HEPA filtration will be running 
 throughout the event. We will update this info when we have it!\n\nThe ven
 ue entrance is wheelchair accessible\, but the bathroom entrance is only 2
  feet wide\, making it non-ADA compliant.\n\nPoster by @ashmademe\n\nCheck
  out our Instagram @offline.recess for more details about each artist and 
 all the activities we’ll have on the day ❤️\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\
 nHosts: Offline Recess\n\nVenue: Sweet Fire Cafe & Studio\n\nEvent page: h
 ttps://luma.com/4yq47j7y
URL:https://luma.com/4yq47j7y
