SUMMARY:2026 A Summer Night in Songs 亞洲彩虹合唱團 夏季演出
LOCATION:Saint Peter's Church - Chelsea\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nA Summer Night in Songs - Asian Rainbow Chorus 
 (ARC) Season 2 Summer Concert\n\nThis summer\, ARC presents a program cent
 ered on resilience\, identity\, and shared hope.\n\nThrough music\, we cel
 ebrate the strength to flourish even in difficult times. In the wake of th
 e pandemic\, amid experiences of discrimination shared by Asian communitie
 s\, and facing a turbulent environment for immigrants\, we choose to respo
 nd through voice rather than silence.\n\nFrom self-affirmation in I Am Wha
 t I Am\,\nto cultural memory in Arirang and Hanyangmen Garden\,\nto poetic
  tenderness in Dirait-on\,\nand culminating in the holiness of Total Prais
 e and Amazing Grace\,\n\nthe concert becomes a journey of remembrance\, in
 tercultural understanding\, and collective uplift.\n\nIn summer light\, we
  sing.\nIn adversity\, we bloom.\n\nProgram\n\nFrom the Start  / 初見\n
 \nMidu Folk Song / 彌渡山歌\n\nHanyangmen Garden / 漢陽門花園\n\n
 Dirait on / 彷彿\n\nI am what I am / 我\n\nArirang / 阿里郎\n\nTotal
  Praise and Amazing Grace / 聖讚 & 奇異恩典\n\n🎟️ Tickets\n\n$1
 2 Early Bird Admission\n\n$15 General Admission\n\n$30 Donation Bundle (in
 cluding ARC merch!)\n\nAbout Us\n\nWe are the Asian Rainbow Chorus (ARC)\,
  founded in New York in July 2024. ARC is an Asian LGBTQ+ choir that cente
 rs on Mandarin-speaking Asians and is dedicated to building connections am
 ong overseas communities.\n\nThe Asian Rainbow Chorus (ARC) is a registere
 d 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization\, fiscally sponsored by SilkPride.\n\nT
 hrough music\, we unite as a community — using our voices to express que
 er identity\, cultural diversity\, and transnational solidarity. ARC is de
 dicated to creating an inclusive space for Mandarin-speaking queer Asians\
 , where members from diverse regions and backgrounds can share their stori
 es\, emotions\, and strength through song.\n\nSinging is also a form of di
 rect action. ARC believes in the power of collective voice and remains com
 mitted to advancing social justice through music.\n\nInstagram: @AsianRain
 bowChorus\nWebsite: https://asianrainbowchorus.org/\n\n💖Support Us\n\nD
 onate: https://givebutter.com/silkpride_ARC2026?s=vUFNPq\n\nPartners\n\nSi
 lkPride\nIn this great voyage of Chinese queer solidarity\, we set sail wi
 th you.\nQueer Chinese + local communities.\nPreserve. Participate. Pass O
 n.\nWebsite: silkpride.org\nInstagram: @silkpride\n\nUnited Proud Women (U
 PW)\nDedicated to serving and supporting sexual and gender minorities with
  female life experiences through knowledge production\, community building
 \, and social advocacy.\nWebsite: upwomxn.org\nInstagram: @upwomxn\n\n「
 夏夜如歌」- 亞洲彩虹合唱團第二樂季夏季音樂會\n\n今
 年夏天，ARC 以「夏夜如歌」為主題，在光與聲音中表達
 生命的力量。\n\n夏天象徵盛放，也像徵在挑戰中依然綻
 放的勇氣。面對疫情後的記憶，亞洲社群共同經歷的誤
 解與歧視，以及移民在當下環境中面對的挑戰，我們選
 擇讓歌聲打破沉寂，用音樂回應現實。\n\n從《I Am What I A
 m》盡情恣肆的自我表達，\n到《Arirang》與《漢陽門花園
 》溫暖親切的文化記憶，\n從《Dirait-on》的詩意與溫柔，
 \n到《Total Praise and Amazing Grace》的聖潔與寧靜，\n\n這是
 一段關於身分、連結與希望的旅程。\n\n在盛夏之中，我
 們歌唱；\n在逆境之中，我們綻放。\n\n演出曲目\n\n初見 
 / From the Start\n\n彌渡山歌 / Midu Folk Song\n\n漢陽門花園 / Han
 yangmen Garden\n\n彷彿 / Dirait on\n\n我 / I am What I am\n\n阿里郎 
 / Arirang\n\n聖讚 & 奇異恩典 / Total Praise and Amazing Grace\n\n
 🎟️ Tickets\n\n$12 Early Bird Admission\n\n$15 General Admission\n\n$3
 0 Donation Bundle (including ARC merch!)\n\n關於我們\n\n我們是 亞
 洲彩虹合唱團（Asian Rainbow Chorus\, ARC），於 2024 年 7 月成
 立於紐約。\nARC 是一支以華語使用者為核心的亞洲 LGBTQ+ 
 合唱團，致力於連結海外社群、凝聚跨地域的酷兒力量
 。\n\n亞洲彩虹合唱團（ARC）以 501(c)(3) 非營利組織 形式
 運作，並由 SilkPride 擔任財務掛靠機構。\n\n透過音樂，
 我們凝聚成一個社群——用歌聲表達酷兒身份、文化多
 樣性與跨國團結。ARC 致力於為講中文的亞洲酷兒群體打
 造一個包容、安全的空間，讓來自不同地區與背景的成
 員能透過歌唱分享故事、情感與力量。\n\n歌唱也是一種
 直接行動。ARC 相信集體的聲音能推動社會正義，並持續
 以音樂作為行動的力量。\n\nInstagram：@AsianRainbowChorus\n网
 站：https://asianrainbowchorus.org/\n\n💖 支持我們\n\n捐助链接
 ：https://givebutter.com/silkpride_ARC2026?s=vUFNPq\n\n合作夥伴\n\nSi
 lkPride\n在這華人同運的大航海時代，和你一起揚帆啟航
 。\nQueer Chinese + local communities.\nPreserve. Participate. Pass On.\n
 Website: silkpride.org\nInstagram: @silkpride\n\nUnited Proud Women (UPW)\
 n致力於透過知識生產、社群建設與社會倡議，服務並支
 持具有女性生命經驗的性少數群體。\nWebsite: upwomxn.org\nIn
 stagram: @upwomxn\n\nCalendar: ARC\n\nHosts: Asian Rainbow Chorus\, Arco\,
  Silkpride\, Manager\n\nVenue: Saint Peter's Church - Chelsea\n\nEvent pag
 e: https://luma.com/lk0peujn
URL:https://luma.com/lk0peujn
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
