SUMMARY:Svarini X Kaho Present: RECLAMATION
LOCATION:Hamilton Loft Red Hook\, Brooklyn\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nCELEBRATING SVARINI'S 3RD BIRTHDAY AND MOKSHA'S
  2-YEAR ANNIVERSARY\n\nJuly 11\, 2026 For one night only\, we're transform
 ing a Brooklyn warehouse into Svarini World.\n\nPart fashion show. Part da
 nce party. Part art installation. Part film screening.\n\nSvarini means fr
 ee woman. RECLAMATION is a celebration of everything we're taking back and
  the party we throw to claim it.\n\n✧ WHAT TO EXPECT ✧\n\nAt 9 PM shar
 p\, we'll debut the newest Svarini collection on the runway in an immersiv
 e fashion presentation featuring 11 looks created for July 11.\n\nAfter th
 e show\, the space opens into a night of exploration:\n\n✧ The Svarini P
 op-Up\nShop exclusive pieces\, archive favorites\, and in-person-only drop
 s.\n\n✧ Moksha Screening Room\nA special screening installation celebrat
 ing the 2-year anniversary of Moksha\, Svarini's debut award-winning short
  film. Screenings will run throughout the evening.\n\n✧ Kaho's Undergrou
 nd Magazine Experience\nFeaturing the latest issue release alongside inter
 active collage\, scrapbook\, and photo moments.\n\n✧ Bad Bindi First Loo
 k\nBe among the first to experience our newest project before its official
  launch.\n\n✧ Glitter Bar\nBecause some problems can\, in fact\, be solv
 ed with more glitter.\n\n✧ DJs\, Dancing\, Food & Drinks\nThe night tran
 sitions from fashion presentation into full celebration mode. Expect good 
 music\, good people\, and enough memories to carry you through the rest of
  the summer.\n\n✧ Photo Moments & Installations\nWe've spent months buil
 ding worlds inside this space. Explore\, wander\, take photos\, make frien
 ds\, and stay awhile.\n\n✧ DRESS CODE: SCANDINAVIAN SCARF ✧ show us ho
 w it's done bb.\n\nThe Pinterest mood board: https://pin.it/2xg5avj58\n\nI
 f you've been waiting for an excuse to wear the outfit sitting in your cam
 era roll\, this is it. No\, you're not overdressed.\n\n✧ EVENT TIMELINE 
 ✧\n\n8:00 PM — Doors Open\n\n9:00 PM — FASHION SHOW (arrive early fo
 r seating)\n\n9:30 PM — Activations\, shopping\, screenings\, DJs\, and 
 installations open in full\n\n11:30 PM — Transition into dance party mod
 e\n\n1:00 AM — Event Ends\n\nThe fashion show begins promptly at 9 PM.\n
 \nIf you arrive late\, you'll miss it.\n\n✧ VIP EXPERIENCE ✧\n\nVIP Ad
 mission Includes:\n\n• Reserved front-row runway seating\n• Reserved f
 irst Moksha screening access\n• Personalized name card\n• Two complime
 ntary drinks\n• Exclusive printed Kaho zine experience\n• Curated VIP 
 goodie bag\n\nIncluding:\n\n• Custom tote\n• Multi-brand samples\n• 
 Kaho zine bundle\n• Additional surprises\n\nVIP capacity is extremely li
 mited.\n\n✧ IMPORTANT ✧\n\nTickets help us bring this experience to li
 fe and keep independent art\, fashion\, and community events accessible.\n
 \nWe only do this once a year. Come dressed up. Bring your friends. We'll 
 handle the rest.\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: Sheel\, apoorva\n\nVenue:
  Hamilton Loft Red Hook\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/wsrlu9py
URL:https://luma.com/wsrlu9py
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
