SUMMARY:MEARI NORI Vol.1 : Korean Culture Playground
LOCATION:NOFLEX® NYC\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nExperience Korea in the heart of NYC — a live
 ly Korean Culture Playground with performance\, K-beauty\, food\, drinks\,
  and live DJ sets.\n\nMEARI NORI Vol.1 : Korean Culture Playground\n\nThe 
 echo of Korea arrives in the heart of New York.\n\nIn Korea\, there's a wo
 rd — '놀이 (Nori)': coming together to enjoy a show\, share food and d
 rinks\, and lose yourself in the moment. It's the liveliest way to experie
 nce Korean culture.\n\nOn July 12th\, Meari — a Korean Culture Collectiv
 e — brings that spirit to the heart of Manhattan.\n\nFrom the deep\, hau
 nting tones of the daegeum (Korean bamboo flute) to the elegant movement o
 f Korean contemporary dance\, the bold procession of a traditional royal m
 arching band\, and a live DJ to heat up the night — the stage flows with
 out pause\, between tradition and modernity\, while the flavors of Korean 
 food and drink keep pouring.\n\nOff to one side\, a K-Beauty pop-up brings
  you face-to-face with a curated lineup of cosmetic brands straight from K
 orea.\n\nTradition and modernity\, the joy of watching and the joy of tast
 ing — all echoing in one place. This is Meari Nori\, the Korean Culture 
 Playground. Come play with us!\n\n✦ Sunday\, July 12th\, 2026 · 6PM–1
 1PM\n✦ NOFLEX® NYC\, 286 Fifth Ave\, New York\, NY 10001\n\n✦ Korean 
 Traditional Flute Performance — Woosung Jung\n✦ Korean Traditional Roy
 al Marching Band Performance — Meari Chwitadae\n✦ Korean Contemporary 
 Dance — Joy Lee\n✦ Live DJ — Kain\n✦ MC — Bora\n\n✦ K-Beauty P
 op-up — K-LAB\n✦ Korean Food Pop-up — Market Woori\n✦ Korean Tradi
 tional Makgeolli — Hayansool\n✦ Korean Fusion Food & Cocktail — NOFL
 EX®\n\n✦ Hosted by Meari — Korean Culture Collective\nCurating Korean
  culture\, echoing it across the world.\n\nGeneral Admission - Free\n• A
 ll performances\n• Food & drinks available for purchase\n\nNori Pass - $
 18\n• All performances\n• Welcome goody bag ($50 value)\n\nNori VIP Pa
 ss - $28\n• All performances\n• Special goody bag ($100 value): K-beau
 ty + premium Korean snacks\n• 1 complimentary glass of premium makgeolli
 \n\nNORI VIP Pass Giveaway — Every VIP Pass holder is entered to win. 3 
 winners will each take home a $500 goody bag! (Winners will be drawn and a
 nnounced at the event. Must be present to claim.)\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\
 nHosts: GreenJI\, Meari\, NOFLEX® NYC\n\nVenue: NOFLEX® NYC\n\nEvent pag
 e: https://luma.com/jzhhtoks
URL:https://luma.com/jzhhtoks
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
