SUMMARY:Antimetal Presents: The Odyssey Prescreening
LOCATION:New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nREGISTRATION REQUIRED\n\nTwo days before it hit
 s theaters\, Antimetal is bringing together New York's technical leaders a
 nd engineers for an early screening of Christopher Nolan's The Odyssey.\n\
 nThis one's for the people who keep production running. If you've ever nav
 igated your own systems through monsters\, storms\, and the occasional act
  of the gods\, you'll feel right at home with Odysseus. Nolan's first film
  since Oppenheimer is a story about endurance\, judgment under pressure\, 
 and getting the team home in one piece (sound familiar).\n\nThe film start
 s at 7:30\, so come early\, meet your peers\, then settle in for the scree
 ning.\n\nCalendar: Antimetal\n\nHosts: Charlie ONeil\, Yohan Sudheer\n\nEv
 ent page: https://luma.com/unxb9qa9
URL:https://luma.com/unxb9qa9
