SUMMARY:Recess at Night: Chapter 2
LOCATION:526 Hudson St\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nTake a break from work with a night of play! \n
 \nJoin Chapter\, a social club for creative connection\, for...\n\nRecess 
 at Night!\n\nWe're back at Anew again for an evening of Recess-style activ
 ities\, all while making new connections and engaging your creativity at A
 new\, a gathering space and discovery center for the social impact communi
 ty located in the West Village.\n\nRecess at Night! is hosted by Ben Mills
