SUMMARY:Meet us on the Roof! Brits in Tech & The Great British Business Clu
 b
LOCATION:New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nSummer Networking “Rooftop Happy Hour”\n\nB
 rits in Tech\, is once again joining forces with The British Consulate Gen
 eral’s Great British Business Club.\n\nThis time for a Happy Hour to cel
 ebrate summer\, co-hosted by Pinpointe Group and Imera.\n\nJoin us for roo
 ftop drinks\, conversations\, and networking with representatives from the
  British Consulate and the wider British business community as we welcome 
 the best of NYC's summer.\n\nYour Hosts:\n\nThe UK’s Department for Busi
 ness and Trade (DBT) helps businesses export\, drives inward and outward i
 nvestment\, negotiates market access and trade deals\, and champions free 
 trade.\n\nFind out more about the British Consulate’s Great British Busi
 ness Club.\n\nPinpointe Group is a NYC-based real estate brokerage that wo
 rks closely with high-growth companies to support employee relocations to 
 New York. We partner with People Ops and leadership teams to help non-loca
 l hires land in NYC quickly\, smoothly\, and ready to work—so relocation
  doesn’t become a distraction from performance\, culture\, or retention.
 \n\nImera is building the go-to platform for immigrants to navigate life i
 n the U.S.\, offering personalized AI-driven guidance\, streamlined access
  to essential services\, and a welcoming community.\n\nBrits in Tech is th
 e home of British tech & startups overseas. A community of founders\, oper
 ators\, engineers and investors — building in NYC\, shipping worldwide.\
 n\nCalendar: Brits in Tech\n\nHosts: Tori Hanson\n\nEvent page: https://lu
 ma.com/qmki592i
URL:https://luma.com/qmki592i
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
