 h technique while helping you craft smart\, sharp visual jokes. No artisti
 c skills required.\n\n🕰️ After Hours at 190 Bowery is our summer even
 t series bringing together people\, brands\, and ideas worth showing up fo
 r.\n\n🏙️ Built in 1898 as Germania Bank and later home to artist Jay 
 Maisel for nearly five decades\, 190 Bowery has long carried the creative 
 spirit of downtown New York.\n\n🎟️ This event is complimentary to att
 end. RSVPs are required but do not guarantee admission\, so we recommend a
 rriving early. Doors open at 6:00pm\, event begins 6:30pm.\n\n🍷 Admissi
