SUMMARY:Creator Economy NYC's July Mixer & Panel
LOCATION:New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nWelcome to Creator Economy NYC — the capital 
 of the creator economy\, where creators\, marketers and founders meet\, le
 arn and earn.\n\nSummer is in full swing and after a packed few months of 
 events\, launches\, conferences\, and creator chaos\, we're bringing the c
 ommunity back together.\n\nJoin Creator Economy NYC and our friends at Top
 Fan for an evening of networking\, conversation\, and connection with crea
 tors\, marketers\, platforms\, and industry leaders shaping what's next.\n
 \nWe'll explore what it means to build a creator business that lasts\, fro
 m audience ownership and direct fan relationships to creating opportunitie
 s beyond the platforms we rely on every day.\n\nExpect networking\, though
 tful discussion\, and the kind of people who make this industry worth bein
 g part of.\n\nApply to join us. More details to follow.\n\nMeet Creator Ec
 onomy NYC \n\nCreator Economy NYC is the capital of the creator economy\,
  where creators\, marketers\, and operators meet\, learn\, and earn. We ho
 st industry-leading panels\, mixers\, and curated dinners with industry co
 nversations that shape the future of the creator economy.\n\nFollow us on 
 Linkedin & Instagram.\n\nMeet Our Presenting Partner\n\nTopFan helps creat
 ors build direct relationships with their audience through branded website
 s and mobile apps that bring content\, community\, and monetization into o
 ne place.\n\nBy giving creators greater ownership of their audience and bu
 siness\, TopFan helps reduce reliance on ever-changing platforms and algor
 ithms.\n\nGet started today.\n\nMeet Our Supporting Partners\n\nAdobe Expr
 ess is Adobe’s all-in-one\, creator-friendly design platform that makes 
 it easy to turn ideas into high-quality content\, fast.\n\nFrom social pos
 ts to videos to branded assets\, it gives creators\, marketers\, and small
  teams the power of Adobe in a simple\, intuitive workflow. It’s built f
 or anyone who wants pro-level visuals without the heavy lift.\n\nGet start
 ed for free.\n\nSiftsy is the social insights platform that enables deep a
 nalysis of comment sections\, helping social teams analyze the response to
  campaign launches\, viral posts\, crises\, or major cultural moments\, wi
 thout the manual lift.\n\nCapture the insights here.\n\nDisclaimers:\n\nCr
 eator Economy NYC events are not first come\, first served. Submitting an 
 RSVP does not guarantee admission.\n\nConfirmed attendees will receive a f
 ollow-up once details and capacity are finalized.\n\nRSVP acceptance is no
 t guaranteed\, and RSVP approval is required for event entry.\n\nBy signin
 g up for the event you will also be subscribed to Creator Economy NYC's we
 ekly newsletter for future event updates.\n\nThis event will be photograph
 ed and Creator Economy NYC\, and all partners reserve the right to use pho
 tos and video from the event for marketing and communications purposes. By
  attending the event\, you consent to the use of your image for these purp
 oses.\n\nCalendar: Creator Economy NYC\n\nHosts: Brett Dashevsky\n\nEvent 
 page: https://luma.com/5crceyl8
URL:https://luma.com/5crceyl8
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
