DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nHey NYC Area AI enthusiasts! Ready to connect\,
  learn\, and have some fun? Join us for The NYC Area Hacking Agents meetup
  hosted by OpenRAG and IBM.\n\nWhether you're an AI developer\, engineer\,
  or just someone excited to learn more\, this meetup is the perfect spot t
 o mingle\, share ideas\, and geek out about all things AI.\n\nJoin us for 
 a night of code\, learning\, and presentations by developers and AI enthus
 iasts who are building. 👩‍💻\n\n🍕Light refreshments will be serv
 ed!\n\n🍻And for those who attend\, there will be an off-site post-event
  drinks gathering.\n\nInterested in speaking here or a future meetup? App
 ly here.\n\nWe have an awesome line up of and a host of tools to help leve
 l up your AI game:\n\nAgenda\n\n5:00 p.m. - Doors open (Grab a bite and do
