LOCATION:222 Grand St\, Brooklyn\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nRace weekend starts here.\n\nJoin us at Brookly
 n Running Co. in Williamsburg for an easy shakeout before Sunday's BKLYN M
 ILE. Shake out your legs\, preview the Kent Ave. course\, and soak in the 
 energy with the NYC running community.\n\nHOKA will have product demos on 
 hand and we'll have coffee to fuel the morning. More activations and detai
 ls to come.\n\nAs we get closer to race day\, we'll send a link with every
 thing you need to know.\n\n📍 Brooklyn Running Co. · 222 Grand St\, Wil
 liamsburg\n🗓 Saturday\, August 1 · 10:00 AM\n\nCalendar: NYC Running E
