LOCATION:190 Bowery\, New York\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin Industrious and Yikes Comedy for standup c
 omedy night at 190 Bowery\, the historic downtown building now home to Ind
 ustrious.\n\n🕰️ After Hours at 190 Bowery is our summer event series 
 bringing together people\, brands\, and ideas worth showing up for.\n\n
 🏙️ Built in 1898 as Germania Bank and later home to artist Jay Maisel
  for nearly five decades\, 190 Bowery has long carried the creative spirit
  of downtown New York.\n\n🎟️ This event is complimentary to attend. R
 SVPs are required but do not guarantee admission\, so we recommend arrivin
 g early. Doors open at 6:00pm\, event begins 6:30pm.\n\n🍷 Admission inc
 ludes one complimentary drink and light snacks. Non-alcoholic options are 
 sponsored by Culture Pop.\n\nMust be 21+ to attend.\n\nAbout Industrious\n
 \nIndustrious is the world’s leading workplace experience company. We ma
 ke workplaces welcoming\, empowering\, and delightful\, and create enrichi
 ng experiences for individuals and teams of all sizes. Our flexible offeri
 ngs include dedicated offices\, turnkey private suites\, and on demand acc
 ess to coworking and meeting spaces.\n\nCalendar: Industrious\n\nHosts: 19
